&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt? **Zowie**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: Gothic?? ?Century 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE:&gt;does not mean that they will eventually be implemented however it does mean that the class as a whole still feels that these are valid issues and would like implementation eventually.&amp;nbsp; One thing to &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt? **Zowie**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: Gothic?? ?Century 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE:&gt;note, we will not be responding to requests as to why something is classified the way it is.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt? **Zowie**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: Gothic?? ?Century 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: Gothic?? ?Century 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE:&gt;This post will be locked and updated bi-weekly.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt? **Zowie**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: Gothic?? ?Century 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE:&gt;*************************************************************************************************************&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal auto? mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: 0pt; 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify;&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;1.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;make the AA abilities Turn Undead &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(possible upgrade in Omens)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#000000&gt; &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;and Divine Avatar &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;( currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#000000&gt; useful&lt;B **Zowie**?mso-bidi-font-weight: normal?&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;2.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;fix damage mitigation to that of plate wearers &amp;amp; increase skill caps for dodge, parry, bash, offense, defense, 1HB &amp;amp; 2HB &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;(no change planned at this time)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;3.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;reduce or remove regent cost for spells &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;4.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;improve DD spells – better damage, better mana to damage ratios, lower recycle times, reduce resists &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;(no change planned at this time)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;5.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;self invis spell (fixed duration preferable) &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;(no change planned at this time)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;6.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;increase cleric DPS – both melee and spell &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;7.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;improve undead dots – increase overall damage, reduce chance to fizzle, increase range &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;8.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;undead mez spell and slow &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;(no change planned at this time)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;B **Zowie**?mso-bidi-font-weight: normal?&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;9.&lt;SPAN New ?Times Roman?? **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;group yaulp &lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(no change planned at this time)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
