&lt;P class=MsoNormal mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: list tab-stops: level1 mso-list: 0in lfo1; l0 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: TEXT-ALIGN: justify; .25in? 0.25in; -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT:&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;Ky&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
